1
00:00:50,520 --> 00:00:51,560
It's pretty big

2
00:00:53,799 --> 00:00:55,719
Can't run away now, right?

3
00:00:55,920 --> 00:00:57,759
Minjiang's wedding is a major life event

4
00:00:58,119 --> 00:00:59,039
You asked me for a loan

5
00:00:59,039 --> 00:00:59,960
I didn't make excuses, did I?

6
00:01:00,359 --> 00:01:01,840
I gave you the money without a second thought

7
00:01:01,840 --> 00:01:02,159
Right?

8
00:01:02,159 --> 00:01:02,679
Yes, yes, yes

9
00:01:02,679 --> 00:01:05,280
You said you'd pay me back after collecting the gifts

10
00:01:05,519 --> 00:01:06,480
Now the wedding is over

11
00:01:06,480 --> 00:01:07,400
The gifts have been collected

12
00:01:07,480 --> 00:01:08,599
You should pay me back now

13
00:01:08,599 --> 00:01:09,079
Right?

14
00:01:09,079 --> 00:01:10,879
Otherwise, how can I explain this to my wife?

15
00:01:11,480 --> 00:01:12,439
Old He

16
00:01:12,439 --> 00:01:13,799
Don't be anxious

17
00:01:13,879 --> 00:01:15,439
I'm working on it

18
00:01:15,439 --> 00:01:17,159
Give me some time

19
00:01:17,599 --> 00:01:18,719
Alright, alright

20
00:01:18,719 --> 00:01:20,400
I'll give you three days

21
00:01:29,280 --> 00:01:30,000
Minjiang

22
00:01:30,319 --> 00:01:31,040
This set...

23
00:01:31,280 --> 00:01:33,239
The Four Treasures of the Study my teacher left me

24
00:01:33,760 --> 00:01:34,519
I'm giving it to you

25
00:01:34,760 --> 00:01:35,519
Teacher Zhen

26
00:01:35,840 --> 00:01:36,640
I can't accept this

27
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:37,319
Minjiang

28
00:01:37,480 --> 00:01:39,359
You are my proudest student

29
00:01:39,480 --> 00:01:41,719
For your dedication to learning,

30
00:01:41,760 --> 00:01:43,120
and improvement in skills,

31
00:01:43,359 --> 00:01:44,239
I, as your teacher,

32
00:01:44,599 --> 00:01:46,280
cannot express the comfort

33
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:47,560
and pride in my heart

34
00:01:47,599 --> 00:01:49,879
As my proudest disciple,

35
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:51,799
you deserve a reward

36
00:01:52,719 --> 00:01:53,519
Take this

37
00:01:54,239 --> 00:01:56,159
This is the only valuable thing right now

38
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:59,400
But Teacher Zhen, won't you...

39
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:03,439
Minjiang

40
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:04,879
Your Uncle He...

41
00:02:05,079 --> 00:02:06,640
is here at the house collecting the debt

42
00:02:07,719 --> 00:02:08,240
Mom

43
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:12,199
I'm going out for a bit

44
00:02:30,199 --> 00:02:33,199
Five hundred for this? That's robbery!

45
00:02:36,639 --> 00:02:37,520
Yaomei

46
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:38,840
You're finally here

47
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:40,159
What fish are you selling today?

48
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:41,639
Still crucian carp and grass carp

49
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:43,039
I'll take all these fish

50
00:02:43,639 --> 00:02:44,360
Wait, wait

51
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:45,240
You're taking them all?

52
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:45,719
No, no

53
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:47,400
I agreed with Yaomei yesterday

54
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:48,599
She said she'd sell the fish to me

55
00:02:50,039 --> 00:02:51,520
Then what should we do?

56
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:53,560
I only caught five fish today

57
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:56,120
Two are small ones, less than a jin

58
00:02:56,319 --> 00:02:58,000
We came first, we'll take two

59
00:02:58,000 --> 00:02:59,439
He came later, let him have one

60
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:02,000
Then I'll give you some extra live shrimp

61
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:02,560
Does that work?

62
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:03,719
That works, that works

63
00:03:03,719 --> 00:03:04,159
That'll do

64
00:03:04,159 --> 00:03:05,599
Here, good, come on

65
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:06,400
Thanks

66
00:03:07,039 --> 00:03:08,199
This is too expensive

67
00:03:08,199 --> 00:03:09,199
Who can afford this?

68
00:03:16,560 --> 00:03:18,360
It really pays better than wages.

69
00:03:22,199 --> 00:03:23,039
Zheng Minjiang.

70
00:03:28,039 --> 00:03:30,520
You, a dignified Designated Workshop Director,

71
00:03:30,719 --> 00:03:32,759
how come you're running a street stall too?

72
00:03:33,919 --> 00:03:34,960
None of your business!

73
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:42,120
I catch fish all day and only earn five sixty.

74
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:44,439
You want five hundred for this lousy brush?

75
00:03:44,560 --> 00:03:45,960
Are you playing Jiang Taigong?

76
00:03:46,479 --> 00:03:47,479
What do you know?

77
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:49,400
My Four Treasures of the Study are worth this price.

78
00:03:50,319 --> 00:03:51,840
If you don't understand, don't talk nonsense here.

79
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:53,560
Fair point.

80
00:03:54,199 --> 00:03:56,240
You racked up a buttload of debt for your wedding,

81
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:57,599
so you're desperate enough to take that thing

82
00:03:57,599 --> 00:03:58,520
and sell it for five hundred.

83
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:59,439
It's understandable.

84
00:03:59,759 --> 00:04:01,960
But you have to be realistic.

85
00:04:02,199 --> 00:04:03,520
If you ask for ten thousand,

86
00:04:03,639 --> 00:04:04,360
and you can't sell it,

87
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:05,800
isn't it just a waste of breath?

88
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:06,800
If you ask for two yuan,

89
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:09,280
that's real money tucked in your pocket.

90
00:04:09,639 --> 00:04:10,960
Two yuan?

91
00:04:11,879 --> 00:04:13,400
I'm just giving an example.

92
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:14,960
Why get so worked up?

93
00:04:19,879 --> 00:04:20,879
Mr. Wu.

94
00:04:25,439 --> 00:04:26,160
Forget it.

95
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:27,720
To stop your mom

96
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:29,199
from coming to my house to make trouble,

97
00:04:29,199 --> 00:04:30,519
I'll help you out this once.

98
00:04:31,560 --> 00:04:32,360
Give it to me.

99
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:33,279
What are you doing?

100
00:04:33,879 --> 00:04:34,480
What are you doing?

101
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:35,240
Mr. Wu!

102
00:04:35,319 --> 00:04:35,920
Come here, come here.

103
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:36,680
Let me tell you something.

104
00:04:37,279 --> 00:04:38,360
Good stuff, good stuff.

105
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:39,560
Let me show you something good.

106
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:40,560
What is it?

107
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:43,040
Four Treasures of the Study.

108
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:43,879
Yes.

109
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:45,319
It comes with so many brushes.

110
00:04:45,319 --> 00:04:46,000
This hair...

111
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:47,360
might even be tiger hair.

112
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:49,480
And look how good this inkstone is.

113
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:51,000
Two hundred yuan.

114
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:51,600
How about it?

115
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:52,480
Two hundred?

116
00:04:53,279 --> 00:04:54,959
Then I've really found a treasure.

117
00:04:56,319 --> 00:04:57,279
Here, for you.

118
00:04:57,279 --> 00:04:57,680
Okay.

119
00:04:57,879 --> 00:04:58,480
Thank you.

120
00:04:58,759 --> 00:04:59,519
Here, for you.

121
00:05:03,759 --> 00:05:04,399
It's yours.

122
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:11,399
You sold it for just two hundred?

123
00:05:11,399 --> 00:05:11,959
That's right.

124
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:13,000
You...

125
00:05:13,519 --> 00:05:15,480
That Mr. Wu who sells old books...

126
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:16,839
is the most likely person around here

127
00:05:16,839 --> 00:05:18,480
to buy your Four Treasures of the Study.

128
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:19,879
He's the only one with that interest.

129
00:05:19,879 --> 00:05:21,439
I even helped you jack up the price.

130
00:05:21,439 --> 00:05:23,399
Sold it for a whopping two hundred.

131
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:25,079
I thought he was going to haggle with me,

132
00:05:25,079 --> 00:05:26,480
but he just pulled out the cash and paid me.

133
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:28,600
What is it? I helped you out.

134
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:29,759
How are you going to thank me?

135
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:30,959
Thanks a lot.

136
00:05:31,639 --> 00:05:34,000
My dear girl.

137
00:05:35,759 --> 00:05:36,360
Wait a second.

138
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:37,199
What's wrong?

139
00:05:37,399 --> 00:05:38,560
Mr... Mr. Wu.

140
00:05:38,879 --> 00:05:39,560
I'm sorry.

141
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:41,480
About the Four Treasures of the Study...

142
00:05:41,639 --> 00:05:42,720
I'm not selling it for the time being.

143
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:44,360
A famous inkstone, clear water...

144
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:45,680
ancient ink, freshly ground.

145
00:05:46,319 --> 00:05:48,160
A crystallization of history and art.

146
00:05:48,319 --> 00:05:50,000
A vessel of cultural heritage.

147
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,399
I can see that.

148
00:05:51,839 --> 00:05:52,519
This item...

149
00:05:52,879 --> 00:05:54,920
is a rare treasure, hard to come by.

150
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:56,439
I know.

151
00:05:56,639 --> 00:05:57,560
You've parted with something you love.

152
00:05:58,120 --> 00:06:00,959
But I also treasure such things like my life.

153
00:06:01,319 --> 00:06:02,399
I hope you can grant me this.

154
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:08,160
I...

155
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:10,680
You didn't tell me

156
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:11,720
that thing was worth five hundred.

157
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:12,600
Or even more.

158
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:14,040
How was I supposed to know?

159
00:06:14,319 --> 00:06:15,439
I didn't say?

160
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:16,480
On this sign of mine,

161
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:17,920
didn't it say five hundred?

162
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:18,680
But you...

163
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:21,759
Forget it.

164
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:24,360
We just can't see eye to eye.

165
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:26,040
Since it's already sold,

166
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:26,959
thanks a lot.

167
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:29,279
No good deed goes unpunished.

168
00:06:29,279 --> 00:06:30,279
Why do I even bother?

169
00:06:30,279 --> 00:06:31,199
From now on, when I see Zheng Minjiang,

170
00:06:31,199 --> 00:06:32,399
I'll just steer clear, alright?

171
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:34,759
You're the one getting angry?

172
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:41,240
Seductress

173
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:42,680
Seducing men

174
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:44,360
The second Wang daughter, Wang Yingrong

175
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:45,959
You seductress, get out here!

176
00:06:46,319 --> 00:06:47,600
Yingrong seduced someone?

177
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:48,800
How is that possible?

178
00:06:48,879 --> 00:06:50,079
Yingrong doesn't seem like that kind of person.

179
00:06:50,079 --> 00:06:51,120
The second Wang daughter...

180
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:52,199
She's really a piece of work.

181
00:06:52,199 --> 00:06:53,120
Just the other day,

182
00:06:53,639 --> 00:06:55,279
I was thinking of introducing my nephew to her.

183
00:06:55,879 --> 00:06:56,920
Good thing I didn't say anything.

184
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:58,199
Sister Chen,

185
00:06:58,199 --> 00:06:59,839
you were right not to say anything.

186
00:06:59,839 --> 00:07:00,839
Otherwise,

187
00:07:00,839 --> 00:07:02,120
your family

188
00:07:02,519 --> 00:07:04,439
would have had bad luck for eight lifetimes.

189
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:08,199
Everyone, come judge for yourselves!

190
00:07:08,199 --> 00:07:09,519
You can't bully people like this!

191
00:07:09,519 --> 00:07:11,079
Yingrong has been good since childhood. It's impossible.

192
00:07:11,079 --> 00:07:11,920
Sister,

193
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:13,439
let's go inside to talk.

194
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:14,439
Is there anything

195
00:07:14,439 --> 00:07:16,319
that can't be said in front of everyone?

196
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:18,439
I'm not the one with a guilty conscience.

197
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:19,720
Don't be angry.

198
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:20,360
Don't be angry.

199
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:21,040
Look at you,

200
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:22,480
what kind of mother are you?

201
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:24,600
Is this how you raise your daughter?

202
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:27,600
Yingrong, you're finally back.

203
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:29,439
This director's wife is no pushover.

204
00:07:29,439 --> 00:07:30,680
Stop making a scene here.

205
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:32,920
It's all because of you, seductress!

206
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:35,439
I'm going to tear your face apart!

207
00:07:35,839 --> 00:07:37,279
You shameless thing!

208
00:07:37,519 --> 00:07:38,480
I didn't seduce him!

209
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:39,839
He harassed me!

210
00:07:39,839 --> 00:07:41,360
This director's wife is too vicious.

211
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:42,959
Exactly, how can she hit people?

212
00:07:42,959 --> 00:07:43,560
Leaders,

213
00:07:47,279 --> 00:07:49,319
there is no justice!

214
00:07:49,319 --> 00:07:50,360
Look at this,

215
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:51,879
with so many people in the factory,

216
00:07:51,879 --> 00:07:54,199
why would I single you out to frame?

217
00:07:54,199 --> 00:07:56,000
Do I have nothing better to do?

218
00:07:56,079 --> 00:07:57,319
If it weren't for this,

219
00:07:57,360 --> 00:07:59,040
would the factory suspend you?

220
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:01,199
Let me tell you,

221
00:08:01,199 --> 00:08:02,560
coming here to make a scene is useless.

222
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:03,360
Apart from anything else,

223
00:08:03,480 --> 00:08:05,279
what I said in those reports to the factory is true.

224
00:08:05,279 --> 00:08:06,399
The factory can investigate all they want,

225
00:08:06,399 --> 00:08:07,680
and I won't withdraw my report.

226
00:08:07,759 --> 00:08:08,800
If you keep making a scene,

227
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:10,160
I'll call the Security Department.

228
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:10,720
Let's go.

229
00:08:11,759 --> 00:08:12,680
Go back.

230
00:08:14,360 --> 00:08:15,839
Don't talk to her anymore.

231
00:08:16,240 --> 00:08:17,480
You shameless thing!

232
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:19,319
You're the mistress and you think you're right?

233
00:08:20,639 --> 00:08:21,759
Just you wait!

234
00:08:23,759 --> 00:08:25,279
This woman is not simple.

235
00:08:25,279 --> 00:08:26,480
Look at how shrewish she is.

236
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:27,839
Could Yingrong have been wrongly accused?

237
00:08:28,199 --> 00:08:29,399
Mom.

238
00:08:32,559 --> 00:08:33,960
You've been suspended?

239
00:08:35,759 --> 00:08:37,360
They are clearly framing me.

240
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:38,039
No.

241
00:08:38,679 --> 00:08:40,039
Your sister is still in school.

242
00:08:40,039 --> 00:08:41,519
You must keep this job.

243
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:44,159
Otherwise, where will the money for her come from?

244
00:08:44,759 --> 00:08:45,399
Tomorrow,

245
00:08:45,399 --> 00:08:46,720
come with me to the factory.

246
00:08:46,720 --> 00:08:48,360
Apologize to Director Zhang and his wife.

247
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:50,799
Beg Manager Liu for mercy.

248
00:08:50,799 --> 00:08:51,440
Mom,

249
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:53,759
I will absolutely not apologize to that Zhang guy.

250
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:05,000
You think this will make me compromise?

251
00:09:05,559 --> 00:09:06,639
Absolutely impossible.

252
00:09:11,759 --> 00:09:13,679
Mom, let go.

253
00:09:14,919 --> 00:09:16,399
I'll walk on my own.

254
00:09:19,039 --> 00:09:20,480
If you want me to reason with them,

255
00:09:20,679 --> 00:09:21,519
I'm going.

256
00:09:21,759 --> 00:09:23,440
But if you want me to apologize,

257
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:24,279
that's impossible.

258
00:09:24,279 --> 00:09:24,879
Yingrong...

259
00:09:24,879 --> 00:09:26,039
Stop bringing up other things.

260
00:09:26,039 --> 00:09:27,320
Just go apologize.

261
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:27,879
I...

262
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:30,840
You... what are you doing?

263
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:33,799
Everyone, look!

264
00:09:33,799 --> 00:09:34,559
Look!

265
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:36,840
Wang Yingrong, this shameless woman!

266
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:38,600
She seduced my Old Zhang!

267
00:09:38,639 --> 00:09:41,559
And yesterday she beat me up like this!

268
00:09:42,879 --> 00:09:43,960
I'm reporting her!

269
00:09:44,559 --> 00:09:45,679
Wang Yingrong, she...

270
00:09:46,159 --> 00:09:47,320
She seduced me!

271
00:09:47,519 --> 00:09:49,240
And filed a false report to slander me!

272
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:51,039
And she beat my wife up like this!

273
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:52,759
Did I do that to you?

274
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:54,720
You faked that yourself!

275
00:09:54,960 --> 00:09:56,279
Since you want to fake it,

276
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:57,440
I...

277
00:09:57,519 --> 00:09:59,279
I'll really hit you then!

278
00:10:01,639 --> 00:10:03,639
I've never seen such a low-quality employee like you!

279
00:10:04,039 --> 00:10:04,799
I'll teach you to talk nonsense!

280
00:10:04,799 --> 00:10:05,360
I'll teach you to lie!

281
00:10:05,360 --> 00:10:06,559
I'm hitting you! Take that!

282
00:10:06,679 --> 00:10:07,320
Stop it!

283
00:10:07,399 --> 00:10:07,840
Stop it!

284
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:08,799
Stop fighting!

285
00:10:10,879 --> 00:10:11,679
Yingrong!

286
00:10:11,679 --> 00:10:12,279
Wang Yingrong.

287
00:10:12,279 --> 00:10:13,679
Your conduct was improper before.

288
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:16,600
The factory only suspended you as punishment.

289
